title: GAP Men's Original Straight Fit Denim Jeans
description: THE ORIGINAL FIT JEANS: These straight fit jeans offer a casually modern look for any outfit
PREMIUM DENIM: Made from soft premium non-stretch denim for total comfort, this pair only gets better over time
CLASSIC DETAILS: These jeans feature classic five-pocket styling, a button closure, and a heavy-duty zipper fly for a timeless look
BETTER DENIM FOR A BETTER PLANET: This pair of denim pants is part of our water conserving Washwell program dedicated to finding more responsible ways to creating the styles we all know and love
AMERICAN STYLE FOR ALL AGES: GAP champions a uniquely optimistic sense of American style that bridges the gaps between individuals, generations, and cultures

Modern American Optimism is in our DNA. Since 1969, we have acted as a force for good. Bridging the gaps between generations, backgrounds, and ideas through the honesty (and hope) of our eternal youthful energy.
